The evidence with the title 'Corporate income tax rates around the world, 2015 - tax foundation ' says Oct 1, 2015  ... It is well known that the United States has the highest corporate income tax rate among the 34 industrialized nations of the Organisation For Economic Co- Operation And Development ( OECD).[1 ] However, it is less well known how the United States stacks up against countries throughout the entire world . 
